@startuml module-call-sequence
autonumber
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ArrowColor #3B82F6
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #10B981

actor Student as "留学生 (Student)"
participant "Frontend SPA" as FE
participant "Express Router" as Router
participant "Auth Middleware" as Auth
participant "Repository Layer" as Repo
database "Database / Storage" as DB
participant "Speech Provider" as Speech

Student -> FE: 触发跟读录音上报 (15秒内 Opus)
FE -> Router: POST /api/v1/recordings (Multipart FormData, JWT)
activate Router
Router -> Auth: 拦截并提取 JWT (assertHomeworkAccess)
activate Auth
Auth --> Router: 鉴权通过 (Identity Verified)
deactivate Auth
Router -> Speech: 上传跟读音频数据执行评测
activate Speech
Speech --> Router: 返回音素级评测百分制成绩
deactivate Speech
Router -> Repo: upsertLearningRecord(RecordDto)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: 比对并无损保存最佳成绩 (ACID 事务)
activate DB
DB --> Repo: 事务执行成功
deactivate DB
Repo --> Router: 返回最佳成绩记录 DTO
deactivate Repo
Router --> FE: 返回 RecordingDto & 评测高亮反馈包
deactivate Router
FE --> Student: 界面渲染 ASR 发音盲区高亮与得分
@endum
